---
title: Spicy Prawn Red Thai Curry with courgette, carrot and rice
description: If you're looking for a dish with flavour, this spicy prawn curry has it in spades. Spicy Thai red curry paste, zesty lime rice, fresh coriander and juicy prawns come together to make a perfectly balanced dish that's bursting with amazing tastes.
